      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>The wearer of a reaper's mask gains a +2 competence bonus on Perception checks made against creatures that aren't immune to fear and a +1 profane bonus on damage with slashing weapons made against living creatures. The wearer can cast confusion twice per day (DC 16). When a reaper's mask is donned, the wearer takes 1 point of Charisma damage-most Skinsaw cultists don their masks well in advance of a mission so they have time to recover.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, confusion, deathwatch</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>AP 102",
